source: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_ULGERIRONHEART_000_000<tab>Hm? That there is a sightseeing log, unless I'm mistaken. Do you perchance know a woman named Millith?
target: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_ULGERIRONHEART_000_000<tab>Sehe ich da etwa ein Exemplar des Eorzea Incognita aus deiner Tasche ragen? Womöglich bist du diese<var 08 E905 (()) ((r)) /var> „außer<var 16 /var>ge<var 16 /var>wöhn<var 16 /var>liche Abenteurer<var 08 E905 ((in)) (()) /var>“, von <var 08 E905 ((der)) ((dem)) /var> Millith geredet hat.

source: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_ULGERIRONHEART_000_001<tab>Hah, what are the odds! Millith is my niece, lest you wonder, and she has told me much and more about you in her letters.
target: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_ULGERIRONHEART_000_001<tab>Also doch! Ich bin Ulger Ironheart und Millith ist meine Nichte, musst du wissen. Wir Ironhearts sind alle vom selben Schlag - wir leben für die Erforschung unbekannter Gebiete.

source: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_ULGERIRONHEART_000_002<tab>Ah, but where are my manners? Ulger Ironheart, at your service. I'm an explorer like most of the clan, and my niece bade me share with you such knowledge I have accumulated. Here, lend me your log.
target: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_ULGERIRONHEART_000_002<tab>Zeig doch dein Eorzea Incognita einmal her. Millith hat mich gebeten, dir ein bisschen auf die Sprünge zu helfen, falls ich dich treffe.

source: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_ULGERIRONHEART_000_003<tab>Let's see now... Definitely there...and there...and there...and <var 1A 02 /var>there<var 1A 01 /var>! Yes, that ought to suffice.

TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_ULGERIRONHEART_000_004<tab>My explorations have taken me far and wide, but dearest to my heart are the regions of Ala Mhigo, beauteous in their ruggedness, and the lands of the Far East, glorious in their diversity.
target: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_ULGERIRONHEART_000_004<tab>Hier, bitte! Ich habe dir ein paar neue Orte notiert, die du unbedingt sehen solltest. Weltbekannte Monumente und absolute Geheimtipps - alles komplett mit Erklärung.

source: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_ULGERIRONHEART_000_005<tab>There are many wondrous sights to be seen in these places, and I've written down the directions to them. Some will prove more difficult to reach than others, but if you're even half as resourceful as Millith says you are, I'm confident that you will find them all.
target: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_ULGERIRONHEART_000_005<tab>Du weißt vielleicht noch nicht so recht, wie du an manche der Orte gelangen sollst, aber ich bin sicher, dass du im Laufe deiner Abenteuer deinen Weg ganz von selbst findest.

source: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_ULGERIRONHEART_000_006<tab>And with that, I shall leave you to resume your adventures. Go forth, my friend, and take in such breathtaking vistas as even my father, the great Roddard Ironheart, could not see in his lifetime!
target: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_ULGERIRONHEART_000_006<tab>Also auf zu neuen Entdeckungen! Du bist wirklich zu be<var 16 /var>glück<var 16 /var>wünschen, dass du so faszinierende Landstriche zu sehen bekommst. Nicht einmal mein Vater, der berühmte Roddard Ironheart, durfte das erleben.

source: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_SYSTEM_000_007<tab>Stormblood entries have been added to your sightseeing log!
target: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_SYSTEM_000_007<tab>Deiner Ausgabe von Eorzea Incognita wurde das Kapitel „Stormblood“ hinzugefügt!

source: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_SYSTEM_000_008<tab>You must be level 60 or above to record Stormblood vistas. Travel to the location indicated and fulfill the necessary conditions and you will complete the entry for that vista, earning experience points in the process.
target: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_SYSTEM_000_008<tab>Du musst die darin enthaltenen Orte als beliebige Klasse oder Job der Stufe 60 oder höher besuchen, um sie freizuschalten und Routine zu erwerben.

source: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_SYSTEM_000_009<tab>Use your wits and the notes provided by Ulger to identify these stunning sights and the proper way to appreciate them, and see Ala Mhigo and the Far East as only the greatest explorers have seen them!
target: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_SYSTEM_000_009<tab>Die groben Hinweise des Reiseführers dienen dir dabei als Leitfaden.

source: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_ULGERIRONHEART_000_020<tab>In my capacity as an explorer, I must inform you that the lands beyond are fraught with danger. If you mean to venture forth, you'd best have the means to protect yourself.
target: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_ULGERIRONHEART_000_020<tab>Das Erforschen und Entdecken liegt uns Ironhearts im Blut! Ich hoffe nur, dass du nicht in Gefahr gerätst, wenn du auf unseren Fußstapfen wandelst. Nimm lieber eine Waffe mit und behalt deine Umgebung gut im Auge.

source: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_SYSTEM_000_021<tab>In order to undertake this quest, you must be a Disciple of War or Magic.
target: TEXT_STMBDY102_02920_SYSTEM_000_021<tab>Um diesen Auftrag fortzusetzen, muss dein Charakter entweder Krieger oder Magier sein.
